Package edu.uab.ssg.io.decode

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FullScoreFileParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed SNP records and problems due to bad record formatting.
    FullScoreFileParser.SNPRecord
    A SNP record.
    GenotypeFileParser.GenotypeRecord
    A genotype record.
    GenotypeFileParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed genotype records and problems due to bad record formatting.
    GTypeFileParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed SNP records and problems due to bad record formatting.
    GTypeFileParser.SNPRecord
    A SNP record.
    SNPFileParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed SNP records and problems due to bad record formatting.
    SNPFileParser.SNPRecord
    A SNP record.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FullScoreFileParser
    A parser for the snps_fullscore_20080328.tab file compiled by Gisli Masson at deCODE and circulated to the UAB popgen team on March 28, 2008.
    GenotypeFileParser
    A parser for the genotype file format used by deCODE to report genotyping results from a custom Illumina SNP array.
    GTypeFileParser
    A parser for the JHY_GType.txt file format from deCODE containing A/B allele calls.
    SNPFileParser
    A parser for the "JHY_SNP.txt" file format.
